          "id": "arc-b04b7b60b2a2638d",
          "text": "Many endangered animals are captured, tagged, and then released back into their environment. The tag may be a piece of coded plastic or metal that is placed somewhere safe on the body. Which is the most likely reason to tag an animal?",
