          "id": "arc-d524437f69c60e28",
          "text": "Scientists have explained how amino acids, carbohydrates, nucleic acids, and fatty acids could all have been synthesized on Earth before living organisms appeared. Which of the following discoveries would most support the claim that life spontaneously generated from these biochemicals?",
