          "id": "arc-f2062ea98c246238",
          "text": "The equation below shows the products formed when a solution of silver nitrate (AgNO3) reacts with a solution of sodium chloride (NaCl). AgNO3 \u0002+ NaCl (Reactants) -> NaNO3 \u0002+ AgCl (Products) In this equation, the total mass of the reactants is",
